title: Total international travellers entering the country in Canada 2020
summary: A line chart of the number of travellers entering Canada .
It starts out high then plummets , and maintains the low level .
gold: The graph demonstrates the total international travelers entering the country in Canada in 2020 and measured in persons as the unit . It begins with a sudden jump ever since the winter has gone from nearly 7e6 to the lowest in April with about 0.5e6 . Then , it follows by some mild fluctuations through the summer and autumn .
